729306f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Avenue - Lamberts Lane
729306f-a.text:
1382 Richmond Avenue, at the S.W. corner of Lamberts
Lane, showing the Our Lady of Pity Roman Catholic Church
(Italian). Note also the Traveling Library, operated by
the Extension Division of the New York Public Library.
August 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
